1.title: Oasis du Vieux Palais de l'Assomption
1.plot: Former courthouse known to be haunted in the Quebec region. Now it serves as a theater, for special events and several other functions. Children would have died in the basement and more.

2.title: Cimetière Abandonné
2.plot: Cemetery of the old village war razed by a flood in the 1900s. The cemetery after several mediums would house several spirits of children who have not found the way to where it should be. I go to the scene with no precise information of the place.

3.title: Asile Abandonné
3.plot: A psychiatric asylum abandoned in the municipality of St-Clotilde de Horton where there were more than 14 dead in total with tragic stories of fire.

imdb.plot outline: Go on an adventure to find the answer to the world of the paranormal. Perhaps discovering a world parallel to ours, trying to understand the unexplained. Close the lights, arm your headphones and dive into the investigation. Be careful. Go to the most famous places to be haunted in the great province of Quebec, armed with his equipment and the night darkness. Michael takes you with him in his quests of the unexplained and tries to communicate with invisible presences. Visits, discoveries, stories and more. This show was made to conclude in the face of the belief of a world parallel to ours towards Michael. Immerse yourself in the fears of darkness and condemned spirits locked in places with sinister stories.
